    "Phase 12 is validation fixture only and performs no server deploy, network, database write, queue creation, auth/secret work, local execution, sends, deploys, or trades.",
    "Server receive records may accept only redacted upload envelope refs with core_sync_safe or already-redacted core_sync_redacted items.",
    "Server receive records may accept only validation-only intent refs pending local Architect acceptance.",
    "Future server store shape may contain redacted summaries, refs, hashes, watermarks, counts, and status summaries only.",
    "Raw comms, raw terminal, screenshot/OCR, browser state, secrets/auth, customer private data, side-profile content, and raw database payloads are blocked.",
    "Profile/session/device scope is required on every receive/status/source ref.",
    "Redaction audits, withheld counts/reasons, and raw stored booleans are required.",
    "Idempotency/replay keys include scope, upload keys, snapshot hashes, watermarks, intent keys, accepted item hashes, and redaction policy.",
    "Missing/regressed watermarks reject; stale uploads warn or reject; stale intents reject.",
    "Server status may report conversation/status/proposal capability while PC is offline, but must honestly say local execution is unavailable.",
    "Server must not claim local execution, PTY, shell, browser/window access, customer-send, deploy, trade, financial action, or model-processing proof.",
    "Bridge is not green from socket alone.",
    "Local Architect is the only future target; direct Builder/Oracle server targeting remains blocked.",
    "Future deletion/export controls are James-visible and redacted-only.",
    "Tests can validate fixture completeness without model calls."
